# Phase 9: Advanced Forensic Intelligence & ID Conflict Awareness

Elevate the system's defensive capabilities by implementing a real-time **Identity Conflict Detection** engine. This phase will allow the system to recognize when a singular biometric profile is associated with multiple distinct passport documents, a critical indicator of sophisticated identity fraud.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This phase introduces a new **Biometric Archive** logic. All new traveler photos processed will be "indexed" (simulated signature stored) to enable future cross-referencing.

- **Forensic Logic**: If a traveler photo matches an existing biometric signature but has a *different* passport number, a **CRITICAL ID CONFLICT** alert will be triggered in the processing center.

